<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="greet-vt">greet <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡriːt/    美 /ɡriːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-welcome">1.★ <strong>打招呼；问候；迎接 (welcome)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>greet the New Year
迎新年</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He greeted his teacher by saying “Good morning!”.
他向老师说了句“早安”。</p></div>

